File: smali_classes2/com/wisky/libnotewritercomponent/utils/WiskyNoteNameUtil$Companion.smali

Full-body rewrite of  createDefaultNoteName(Ljava/util/List;)Ljava/lang/String;

  Before: loops i=1..∞, asks Application.getString(R.string.wisky_component_note_count, i)
          → "Paper 1", "笔记 1" etc., returns first non-duplicate.

  After:  base = new SimpleDateFormat("yy/MM/dd.HH:mm").format(new Date());
          if base not in existNames → return base
          else loop i=1..∞:
              cand = base + " (" + i + ")"
              if cand not in existNames → return cand

